ID number 497-99 (Presentation)
Type: Cultural
Description: This is the google slides presentation regarding the project itself, any issues in the project as well as ways to circumvent admin privileges in the system(s).
Rationale: this will put words and pictures into the project allowing for a better understanding of any issues and how they were fixed and how the project was formed.
